    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Premise</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summer is coming, and you remember all the interesting moments you lived this year at school… that fight in the mud, the organized attack on the kitchen, when we wrecked the teacher’s car, among others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive these adventures one last time with your friends in this Party Game, where you take on the role of a kid with superpowers who just wants to have fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/8bd557cc5b66946b322d2e0df3809d6d.poster.avif?t=1757449197\" width=796 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/8bd557cc5b66946b322d2e0df3809d6d.webm?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/8bd557cc5b66946b322d2e0df3809d6d.mp4?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use objects found on the map during the match, like milk bottles to boost yourself, chili peppers to burn your enemies, potions to turn into a giant, and more gameplay variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/3ebf13b6c9b2184518978d58129fe3ae.poster.avif?t=1757449197\" width=780 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/3ebf13b6c9b2184518978d58129fe3ae.webm?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/3ebf13b6c9b2184518978d58129fe3ae.mp4?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skins</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your style with different skins you can use to show off to your friends that you’re better than them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/9f514264e1421a7296a90632e854d994.avif?t=1757449197\" width=1560 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand the Playground</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you run out of things to do at school, you’ll unlock new games in different locations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/cb14bb54ae730325a30adb401b72c2ce.avif?t=1757449197\" width=1560 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since it’s a party game, there are tons of mini-games to enjoy and master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/649154fda6871ed1c87c98d35b9f07af.poster.avif?t=1757449197\" width=780 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/649154fda6871ed1c87c98d35b9f07af.webm?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219680/extras/649154fda6871ed1c87c98d35b9f07af.mp4?t=1757449197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
